items.name: Sukuti
items.description: Sukuti is a traditional Nepali delicacy made from dried and spiced meat, typically goat or buffalo. It is seasoned with Nepali spices, roasted, and served as a savory snack or in curries. A must-try for lovers of authentic Nepali cuisine.
